     * [https://leanpub.com/saltstackfordevops]Leanpub - SaltStack For
       DevOps by Aymen El Amri.
     * [https://leanpub.com/gettingstartedwithsaltstack]Leanpub - Getting
       Started with SaltStack by Ben Hosmer.
     * [https://www.packtpub.com/networking-and-servers/learning-saltstack
       -second-edition]Packt - Learning SaltStack, 2nd ed. by Colton
       Myers.
     * [https://www.packtpub.com/networking-and-servers/mastering-saltstac
       k-second-edition]Packt - Mastering SaltStack, 2nd ed. by Joseph
       Hall.
     * [https://www.packtpub.com/networking-and-servers/extending-saltstac
       k]Packt - Extending SaltStack by Joseph Hall.
     * [https://www.packtpub.com/networking-and-servers/salt-cookbook]Pack
       t - Salt Cookbook by Anirban Saha.

