Tools

     * [https://github.com/Lothiraldan/saltpad]SaltPad - SaltPad is a GUI
       tool to manage SaltStack deployments + orchestration.
     * [https://github.com/yueyongyue/saltshaker]SaltShaker - Another good
       looking GUI for SaltStack.
     * [https://github.com/maerteijn/SaltGUI]SaltGUI - A web interface for
       managing SaltStack based infrastructure.
     * [https://github.com/webedia-dev/pepperboard]Pepperboard - A simple
       and modular dashboard toolkit for SaltStack.

